snippet.title: OneShot Teaser
snippet.description:
Available on Steam!
http://store.steampowered.com/app/420530/

http://www.oneshot-game.com/
Twitter: @oneshotreboot
Facebook: facebook.com/oneshotreboot
Tumblr: oneshotgame.tumblr.com

Oneshot is a unique Puzzle/Adventure game. You, as the player, must guide Niko through a mysterious world, utilizing items, characters, and the environment to progress.
